Package: deepin-remote-desktop
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Deepin Remote Desktop RDP service
 A GLib-based RDP service providing capture/encoding/input pipeline,
 FreeRDP transport integration, and system/handover daemons for Deepin
 desktop. It targets systemd-managed deployments and ships greeter
 handover helpers plus sample configuration.
